Seventh Age 878 (abbreviated to Se.A. 878) is the 878th year of the Sun of the Seventh Age of Middle-earth.

Notable events in this year include:

Éadwine, the father of Ælfwine sets off in his ship Éarendel and is never seen again.[1]
